116 BT::NodeStatus FilterTomatoQueue::tick()
117 {
118  LOG_MANI_START(this->name());
119  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped manipulator_base_local;
120  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped manipulator_base_map;
121  tf::TransformListener listener;
122  listener.waitForTransform(MAP_FRAME, ARM_BASE_FRAME, ros::Time(0), ros::Duration(3.0));
123  manipulator_base_local.pose.position.x =
124  manipulator_base_local.pose.position.y =
125  manipulator_base_local.pose.position.z = 0.0;
126  manipulator_base_local.header.frame_id = ARM_BASE_FRAME;
127  manipulator_base_local.pose.orientation = tf::createQuaternionMsgFromRollPitchYaw(0, 0, 0);
128  manipulator_base_local.header.stamp = ros::Time();
129  listener.transformPose(MAP_FRAME, manipulator_base_local, manipulator_base_map);
130  int number_of_reachables = tomato_queue_->GetReachableTomatoCount(manipulator_base_map.pose.position.x,
131  manipulator_base_map.pose.position.y,
132  manipulator_base_map.pose.position.z, UR5_WORKING_RADIUS);
133 
134  ROS_INFO("[%s] Printing queue!", this->name().c_str());
135  tomato_queue_->PrintQueue();
136  if (number_of_reachables == 0)
137  {
138  ROS_ERROR("[%s] No more locations!", this->name().c_str());
139  LOG_MANI_STOP(this->name());
140  return BT::NodeStatus::FAILURE;
141  }
142  ROS_INFO("Currently reachable tomatoes: %d", number_of_reachables);
143  setOutput("num_tomatoes", number_of_reachables);
144  LOG_MANI_STOP(this->name());
145  return BT::NodeStatus::SUCCESS;

192 BT::NodeStatus ManipulatorGraspTomato::onStart()
193 {
194  LOG_MANI_START(this->name());
195  BT::Optional<float> tomato_map_x = getInput<float>("target_x");
196  BT::Optional<float> tomato_map_y = getInput<float>("target_y");
197  BT::Optional<float> tomato_map_z = getInput<float>("target_z");
198  if (!tomato_map_x || !tomato_map_y || !tomato_map_z)
199  {
200  ROS_ERROR("GOT NO POSE!");
201  return BT::NodeStatus::FAILURE;
202  }
203  geometry_msgs::Point armlink_loc = ba_helper::GetCurrentArmbaseLocation();
204  float phi = atan2(tomato_map_y.value() - armlink_loc.y, tomato_map_x.value() - armlink_loc.x);
205  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped tomato;
206  tomato.header.frame_id = MAP_FRAME;
207  tomato.pose.position.x = tomato_map_x.value() - sin(phi) * 0;
208  tomato.pose.position.y = tomato_map_y.value() - cos(phi) * 0;
209  tomato.pose.position.z = tomato_map_z.value();
210  tomato.pose.orientation = tf::createQuaternionMsgFromRollPitchYaw(0, 0, 0);
211 
212  manipulator_.MoveGripperToTomato(tomato);
213  return BT::NodeStatus::RUNNING;
214 }
215

280 BT::NodeStatus ManipulatorPregrasp::onStart()

284  BT::Optional<float> tomato_map_y = getInput<float>("target_y");

286  BT::Optional<float> pregresp_offset = getInput<float>("pregrasp_offset");
287  if (!tomato_map_x || !tomato_map_y || !tomato_map_z)

292  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped tomato;
